universum.studios.android.intent

Class PlayIntent

  • java.lang.Object
    • universum.studios.android.intent.BaseIntent<PlayIntent>
      • universum.studios.android.intent.PlayIntent

  • public final class PlayIntent
extends BaseIntent<PlayIntent>
    A BaseIntent builder implementation providing API for building and starting of intents targeting the Android Play Store application.

    This intent builder does not require any of its parameters to be set. Package name of the application component that starts this intent will be used as application Id by default. If this intent is to be started for a specific application, id of that application may be specified via applicationId(String).

    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky
